          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are these aprons made from 100% cotton?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! Each apron is made from <strong>100% natural cotton</strong>, making it soft, breathable, and comfortable to wear while cooking, baking, or crafting.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_PqnTMW": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What makes this apron eco-friendly?",
            "answer": "<p>Our aprons are <strong>hand block printed by artisans</strong> using <strong>eco-conscious dyes</strong> and sustainable cotton fabric. They’re reusable, durable, and a thoughtful alternative to synthetic kitchen wear.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_rchPT3": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is the apron one size fits all?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, it’s <strong>one size fits most adults</strong>, featuring an <strong>adjustable neck strap</strong> and <strong>extra-long waist ties</strong> for a secure and comfortable fit.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_dPhnHC": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does it have pockets?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely! The apron includes <strong>two deep front pockets -</strong> perfect for keeping utensils, recipes, your phone, or towels handy while you work.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_LyzpMg": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How should I wash and care for my apron?",
            "answer": "<p>Machine wash cold with like colors using mild detergent. Tumble dry low or hang to dry. Avoid bleach to preserve the natural fibers and print vibrancy. You can lightly iron on low heat if needed.</p>"
          }
        },
